    <item>
      <title>Fast-Charging Buyer Guides for Van Life (700Wh&#43;)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/fast-charging-buyer-guides/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/fast-charging-buyer-guides/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If any terms feel fuzzy (AC input, surge, pass-through), use the &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/fast-charging-power-station-glossary/&#34; &gt;Fast-Charging Power Station Glossary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;CAVL rule: recommendations start at &lt;strong&gt;700Wh+&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;calv-cta-module&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;calv-cta-row&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a class=&#34;calv-cta&#34; href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/fast-charging-power-station-buyer-checklist/&#34;&gt;Buyer Checklist&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a class=&#34;calv-cta calv-cta-secondary&#34; href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/fast-charging-buyer-guides/&#34;&gt;Buyer Guides&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Start with:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/fast-charging-power-station-buyer-checklist/&#34; &gt;Fast-Charging Power Station Buyer Checklist&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-fast-charging-power-stations/&#34; &gt;Best Fast-Charging Power Stations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Start here (core)&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;start-here-core&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#start-here-core&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-fast-charging-power-stations/&#34; &gt;Best Fast-Charging Power Stations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; — main buyer guide.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&g